						               													<description>Play as a fearsome Dungeon Lord, as you contest against your opponent for spoils. Send your Dungeonling Minions to attack and defend, all the while casting powerful, game-changing spells in an epic battle for victory!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Dungeonling:Battle is a dueling card game in a similar style like Magic:tG, but with its own unique elements. Player must gather resources (the Spoils), and play Minion and Spells cards against each other. However, instead of custom deck, player use a shared deck, and the Spoils can be taken and looted away by attacks. And with the 3-Actions per Turn system, Players also have much more freedom in choosing what strategy to take, and not simply restricted by phases. This creates a more dynamic playing field, where a great hand could win you a comeback and net you the victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Easy to learn, but with deep strategy. It&amp;rsquo;s a great game for both young and casual gamer, as well as card game veteran alike. It's Time to Battle!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
